Product Description

Read more

Product Details:

Type: modern, minimalist wall lamps

Color temperature: 2700K

Materials: gypsum

Light sources and lamp type: G9 LED 7W(Included)

Voltage: AC100-240V

Wattage：7W

Number of LED Lights: 88

Lumen：710

Read more

Gypsum lamp body, durable, one die-casting molding, the details determine the quality! New LED technology, Free 7W LED light bulb which is No Flicker, No Strobe.(You can change the light bulb according to your preference, whether the wattage or the color of the light)

2700K warm white light will give a harmonious and comfortable feeling for your family. Modern and simple wall lamp. It may not be bright enough to be a main light, but it will be really nice decoration, even can be a night light.

Read more

Package included:

* 1 x G9 7W LED Bulb

* 1 x hollow lampshade

* 1 x 4 Screws

* 1 x glove

Product size: 200mm*115mm*85mm

Weight: 1.1kg

Read more

Installation:

1.Make 2 holes in the wall according to the size of the lamp holder.

2.Use 2 screws to secure the lamp holder to the wall.

3.Connect the correct wires to your home circuit.

4. Insert the lamp into the lamp socket and fasten it with a screw.

Installation Tips:

* Suggested to be arranged by the professional electrician when install this wall night light.

* Be careful when installing, please use the gloves to install the light to aviod appearance damage.

* Release two screws of the hanging plate on both sides, take out the hanging plate.

* Drill two holes at right position near the wall wire, set plugs into the hole then fix the hanging plate by screws to the wall.

* Connect the power leads to wall wire and do insulation treatment.

* Fix the lamp fixture on the hanging plate by screwing screws tightly on both sides.
